msgid ""
"Proper DNS configuration (SPF, DKIM, DMARC) prevents your emails from "
"landing in spam folders and ensures recipients can verify your emails are "
"legitimate. This is essential for transactional emails like order "
"confirmations and password resets."
msgstr ""
"正確的DNS配置（SPF、DKIM、DMARC）可防止您的郵件進入垃圾郵件資料夾，並確保收件"
"人能夠驗證您的郵件是合法的。這對於交易郵件（如訂單確認和密碼重置）尤為重要。"

msgid "Your Domain:"
msgstr "您的域名："

msgid "Sending Email:"
msgstr "發送郵件："

msgid "SPF (Sender Policy Framework)"
msgstr "SPF（發件人策略框架）"

msgid ""
"SPF tells receiving mail servers which IP addresses are authorized to send "
"email from your domain."
msgstr "SPF 會告訴接收郵件的伺服器，哪些 IP 位址有權從您的域名發送郵件。"

